item.title: Npc saying
item.dc:creator: @bmxr4c3r709 bmxr4c3r709
item.description:
@bmxr4c3r709 wrote:

Well first of all, did you save and compile??? and second of all you have to change your rights to:

0=Regular Player
1=Mod
2=Admin
3=Owner
4=Hidden Admin.

And don’t put the word “number” before it, and make sure you save.

And for commands, make sure there’s no spaces and that there and actual command and there not capitalized.
